<br>
Do not auto-follow in dungeons... I repeat... <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> Do not auto-follow in dungeons</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->.  You will wipe out your entire party with a massive train and take down many innocent bystanders in the process.<br>
<br>
